{
  "stem": "6130.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- you know, beauty shop has different partitions for dying hair or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we also lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made it in a bedroom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a shower in the basement, and we had a little kitchenette.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- we opened up a business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But to cut the story short, that was in '49.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My son was born in '53.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SOBBING] And by that time, we were building our home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We built our own home in a beautiful neighborhood close to a brand-new elementary school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We worked 10, 12 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the business was just coming in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We couldn't handle it anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to go to another place to rent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we found a building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We bought a building, too, a rundown building in a terrible condition.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when we looked, the-- the roof was leaking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The windows were broken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The building was full with pigeons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But there was a very, very nice Jewish contractor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said, I will fix it up for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, it cost $25,000.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't have enough, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He says, you pay me every month, what you can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't even have to sign a paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were written up in the Rockford paper all the time, by the way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because when we came it was, at that time, something interesting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know how or what, but they found out about how our business was growing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were-- we got a job from a very big publishing company.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can't think of the name of the publisher or the place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You know, the-- a publishing company was in a small town, very small town close to Rockford.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
